{"tid":1648108,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"頂唔順和平耶撚，反問佢點解大衛掟石仔擊殺巨人哥利亞，啞口無言","createTime":"2019-10-12T04:56:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T09:56:04.000Z","uid":294333,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"45e3c5e53af4b62a4e2ddb6248dba085f540e92b","tid":1648108,"uid":294333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n身邊有人係耶撚，叫我禮拜日返下教會祈禱，聽下神嘅話語，然後就展開下列對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：耶撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：本人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每個星期日香港人好忙喎，要嗌下口號<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過嚟聽下聖經，個人會無咁暴力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下？行使暴力嘅政權，警察喎，沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察都係執法啫，唔係全部都衰人，示威者都有掟磚頭，掟燃燒彈燒記者喎，大家和平就無事啦，同教會弟兄姊妹查下聖經，放下仇恨，認識耶和華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我問你，點解舊約聖經裡面，普通嘅牧羊人大衞點解擲石仔反抗巨人哥利亞嘅入侵，仲割斷埋哥利亞人頭，帶去耶路撒冷？ （我心諗 唔好以為我冇讀過聖經啦，小學要考<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />耶和華愛世人，要救佢哋嘛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁香港人唔值得救，咁點解香港唔可以好似大衛咁用石仔擊敗巨人哥利亞？耶和華淨係愛以色列人？摩亞出埃及記，上帝毒死晒埃及長子，過紅海時又淹死埃及人？上帝殺好多人救以色列人？神愛世人，仲咩咁唔和平呀，唔乖乖地服從绯力基人，埃及人，羅馬人下嘅入壓逼統治呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />......如果你想祈禱，搵弟兄姊妹傾偈，有牧師帶領查經茶聚，隨時歡迎你嚟教會㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：聽日10月13日係星期日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aa4ee8097c89b30b4ab82ec8c8354b55ac1959","tid":1648108,"uid":57802,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"講咁多野做乜<br />\n叫佢睇一次出埃及記咪明"},{"pid":"994d50599713eb481e8cb7191c81634cd5bcb57a","tid":1648108,"uid":294333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b9aa4ee8097c89b30b4ab82ec8c8354b55ac1959","tid":1648108,"uid":57802,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"講咁多野做乜<br />\n叫佢睇一次出埃及記咪明"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂，<br />\n經常叫我禮拜返教會，要ko下佢思想，唔好以為我無讀過聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d2e5c39372bbd44a5a0d7e3e11e6539dd36a3d","tid":1648108,"uid":193233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多！"},{"pid":"c4af88b891657d9f4a6a2c7d2aba3a9125014ef4","tid":1648108,"uid":294333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42d2e5c39372bbd44a5a0d7e3e11e6539dd36a3d","tid":1648108,"uid":193233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:17:41.000Z","msg":"巴打似乎都經歷過耶撚邀約<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37b593f9a837a32dabb2a0939b1d6b64b3699ed","tid":1648108,"uid":22310,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"我係耶撚<br />\n同你講嘢個耶撚不代表我們<br />\n咁黑嘅不公義，基督徒反抗責無旁貸"},{"pid":"df13dfbe4fcb5880656e3952e4651e8221e5074d","tid":1648108,"uid":22310,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a37b593f9a837a32dabb2a0939b1d6b64b3699ed","tid":1648108,"uid":22310,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"我係耶撚<br />\n同你講嘢個耶撚不代表我們<br />\n咁黑嘅不公義，基督徒反抗責無旁貸"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"日日喺教會入面避風港，又乜行動都唔做，只係識得一圈人祈禱以為自己做咗啲好特別嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來，祈禱之餘，神係叫我地做實在嘅事"},{"pid":